    • getSaturationPressure

      public static double getSaturationPressure(double temperature)
      Calculate the saturation pressure for CO2 at a given temperature using the Span-Wagner ancillary equation. Valid for temperatures from triple point (216.592 K) to critical point (304.1282 K).
      Parameters:
      temperature - Temperature in Kelvin
      Returns:
      Saturation pressure in Pascal
